    if (isLoading || newValue == '') {
        return;
    }
    g_form.setValue('u_business_phone', '');
    g_form.setValue('u_manager', '');
    g_form.setValue('u_email', '');
    g_form.setValue('u_department', '');
    g_form.setValue('u_select_manager', false);
    g_form.setValue('u_service_location', '');

    var user = g_form.getReference('requested_for_user', callBack);

    function callBack(user) {
        g_form.setValue('u_business_phone', user.phone);
        g_form.setValue('u_manager', user.manager);

        //DIA-4583 - Allow requester to choose manager if user account does not have a manager already listed.
        if (user.manager != '') g_form.setReadOnly('u_manager', true);
        else g_form.setReadOnly('u_manager', false);

        g_form.setValue('u_email', user.email);
        g_form.setValue('u_service_location', user.location);
        g_form.setValue('u_department', user.department);
    }
}]]></script><sys_class_name>catalog_script_client</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>matthew.wise</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-03-06 18:29:03</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>1683ddab19992110e335b07c1fd6fc03</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>onChange requested_for_user </sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Cyber" source="de225cef056b0110e335c1eeddb73836">de225cef056b0110e335c1eeddb73836</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Cyber">de225cef056b0110e335c1eeddb73836</sys_scope><sys_update_name>catalog_script_client_1683ddab19992110e335b07c1fd6fc03</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>matthew.wise</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-03-06 18:29:03</sys_updated_on><table/><type>onChange</type><ui_type>10</ui_type><variable_set/><view/></catalog_script_client></record_update>

        return;

		g_form.setReadOnly('u_business_phone', false);
	}

        //g_form.setReadOnly('u_business_phone', true);

        var user = g_form.getReference('requested_for_user', callBack);
    }

    function callBack(user) {
        g_form.setValue('u_business_phone', user.phone);
    }
}]]></script><sys_class_name>catalog_script_client</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>matthew.wise</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-03-06 18:57:53</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>00b9d1a719d92110e335b07c1fd6fcaa</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Checkbox for Enter an alternate phone</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Cyber" source="de225cef056b0110e335c1eeddb73836">de225cef056b0110e335c1eeddb73836</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Cyber">de225cef056b0110e335c1eeddb73836</sys_scope><sys_update_name>catalog_script_client_00b9d1a719d92110e335b07c1fd6fcaa</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>matthew.wise</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-03-09 13:55:39</sys_updated_on><table/><type>onChange</type><ui_type>10</ui_type><variable_set/><view/></catalog_script_client></record_update>

    }
